org.ensor.data.atom

Class ImmutableList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ensor.data.atom.Atom
      • org.ensor.data.atom.ImmutableList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Atom>, IListVisitable

    public final class ImmutableList
extends Atom
implements Iterable<Atom>
    This class represents a list of immutable objects and the list itself is immutable.

    Jon
